1.title: Experiments
1.plot: Wubbleyoo can't believe it- for the first time ever he doesn't have any questions! So he decides to use his question-answering power to answer some kids' questions. How? By experimenting! Join Wubbleyoo and Lauren as they answer all the questions they can by experimenting!

2.title: Bags
2.plot: Wubbleyoo has SO much stuff! Far too much to carry with just two mousy hands! So Wubbleyoo and Lauren decide the only way to solve the problem is to find out all about bags. From shopping to sleeping to carrying lunch to collecting garbage, join Wubbleyoo and Lauren as they get carried away in this bag adventure!

imdb.plot outline: Wurrawhy is an innovative preschool television show produced by Network Ten. Wubbleyoo (Michael Balk), Lauren, and KB are the three characters that take the audience on an exciting adventure, answering the questions Who, What, When, Where and Why to occupy Wubbleyoo's inquisitive mind! The show airs weekdays on Channel 10 at 7.00 am
